    old "“He used to be able to speak. A sad fate, and a {i}painful{/i} one. One day he ate an undercooked slice of meat on his journey South, and after a few weeks he realized that something was biting his tongue. Something was living in it, like a worm in an apple. We tried to kill it with fire and hard drinks, but it was too late. The flesh started to rot, we had to amputate it. He can’t help other hunters without speaking or shouting, so he’s learning a new trade now.” "
