    old "“{color=#f6d6bd}Bion{/color} the tailor? A quiet one. Everything we wear is from her, this included.” He grabs the bottom part of his tunic and stretches it a bit. “Looks good, don’t you think? Most of the clothes we brought from home got ruined after several years, and our gambesons need a lot of repairs.” He suddenly lets go of his outfit. “Know what? {color=#f6d6bd}Bion{/color} has asked us to bring her any spider silk we find. If you ever get some threads, sell them to her.” "
